# The doc-graph SVG is rendered locally for browsing
# (`node tools/doc-graph/generate.mjs`, needs Graphviz `dot`) and is
# deliberately NOT committed: it re-layouts wholesale on any structural
# change and GitHub counts every line of it (`.gitattributes -diff` does
# not decount on GitHub). The committed manifest `docs/doc-graph.json` is
# the source of truth; `doc-graph-ci` gates that, not the picture. See
# docs/notes/vestige/deferred-items/doc-graph-svg-render-off-tree.md
# (work-status item `doc-graph-svg-render-off-tree`).
docs/doc-graph.svg
